  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A Fool's Art Gallery is a compilation of over 20 years of work by one lone Canadian artist; a 21st Century digital coffee table book; in a first person view 3D virtual space powered by the GZDOOM engine. With a vivid world to explore in and out of the Gallery. In part a psychedelic experience, and a private art gallery for your viewing pleasure. An experimental game aimed more at relaxation of the mind, and an absolute act of cyber escapism. Over 900 works of art, from paintings, to pen and ink drawings, blue prints and designs, digital work, 3 self published books, and a roster of hand drawn NPCs, 4D entities in 3D space, and more!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Coming in the future:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >~More everything. More music, more cats, more art, more secrets, more animation, more NPCs, more more more!!!!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >~Linux version.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >~Spa and lounge levels.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A Fool's Art Gallery is a compilation of over 20 years of work by one lone Canadian artist; a 21st Century digital coffee table book; in a first person view 3D virtual space powered by the GZDOOM engine. With a vivid world to explore in and out of the Gallery. In part a psychedelic experience, and a private art gallery for your viewing pleasure. An experimental game aimed more at relaxation of the mind, and an absolute act of cyber escapism. Over 900 works of art, from paintings, to pen and ink drawings, blue prints and designs, digital work, 3 self published books, and a roster of hand drawn NPCs, 4D entities in 3D space, and more!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Coming in the future:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >~More everything. More music, more cats, more art, more secrets, more animation, more NPCs, more more more!!!!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >~Linux version.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >~Spa and lounge levels.</p>",
